gal is a reference monitor for agentic systems: a minimal, tamper-proof,
verifiable governance kernel. The kernel is open (Apache-2.0); the hosted
control plane (cross-tenant aggregator, billing, multi-tenant operations) is a
separate, proprietary product and is not covered by this license.

If you build on gal, attribution is appreciated — see CITATION.cff.

